{"tid":797944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲男子遭非禮 警緝南亞色狼","createTime":"2018-08-29T02:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T00:01:23.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdedda9319c7a271b02ed92eb51bcc1cf777f0c","tid":797944,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"一名22歲男子，凌晨零時許，在元朗同樂街一單位內，懷疑被一名南亞男子非禮。警員到場經初步調查，案件列作非禮，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n涉案南亞男子年約35歲至40歲、約1.8米高、蓄深黑短髮、案發時身穿淺色上衣、深色長褲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180829/58619294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180829%2F58619294&d=%2F7PvxGVesDDcZSZb%2Fw0AhZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ce8c1bbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180829%2F58619294&h=a186c670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180829/58619294</a>"},{"pid":"67868ecc3a278729327499ef0beee37a41f2411b","tid":797944,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f8ace6188381beac9dda25ac82cd890eebf3cde","tid":797944,"uid":156194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"南亞狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a35f249556c16b152802462531d42bd7731b97","tid":797944,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"元朗<br />\n<br />\n一單位內"},{"pid":"5bc7204abf960117f026d810e4d40691ba21ed9e","tid":797944,"uid":66811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T00:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.drivenachodrive.com/wp-content/uplo